  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">This unsigned letter to Deborah Weston is presumably from one of her sisters. The writer asks Deborah to find and send her riding-habit to her.</subfield>
  </datafield>
  <datafield tag="500" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="a">The end of this letter is missing. This letter is written on the verso of a torn flier (printed matter) of an invitation to Music Hall on Wednesday evening, Jan. 23.</subfield>
  </datafield>
